{"tid":2283623,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"過咗兩日，好似又無咁掛住kelly咁","createTime":"2020-11-12T17:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T17:53:52.000Z","uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b54f0d5bc61d3bbd2c698cc88e0601e73147a940","tid":2283623,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T17:14:16.000Z","msg":"其實本身已經唔會刻意諗起佢，就算諗返起都唔會有好大感覺，但係一夢見佢真係搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟有冇方法可以避免再夢到佢，其實對佢已經唔會再抱有任何幻想同期望，我同佢對上一次曖昧之間足足隔咗成4年，我真係冇咁多嘅時間去放喺一個只係當我水泡嘅人，求下大家<br />\n<br />\n人若變唔想再愛kelly啦，<br />\n教我，<br />\n點樣，<br />\n可以，<br />\n唔好，<br />\n再夢到，<br />\nkelly啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但不夠迷人再記抑裏面<br />\n才知道人若變很想講再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0004053fbb7dc12fd50922bb6073ae60b9c86a","tid":2283623,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T17:15:20.000Z","msg":"真正放下 就不會再夢到了"},{"pid":"facd994927ccf6d1cf51f0d58dacb788c85ce01f","tid":2283623,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T17:17:12.000Z","msg":"佢琴晚鬧得你啱唔啱？"},{"pid":"22a81649f4925dcb90416eab4007f882472fbf67","tid":2283623,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f0004053fbb7dc12fd50922bb6073ae60b9c86a","tid":2283623,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T17:15:20.000Z","msg":"真正放下 就不會再夢到了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T17:17:54.000Z","msg":"我都以為自己放低咗 都成個月啦其實 點知就殺出個咁嘅垃圾夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9c06b032a78b7e51a9fe2a11e9484e8bb0aa17","tid":2283623,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"facd994927ccf6d1cf51f0d58dacb788c85ce01f","tid":2283623,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T17:17:12.000Z","msg":"佢琴晚鬧得你啱唔啱？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T17:20:20.000Z","msg":"唔啱呀屌你老母<